      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HE'S REGAL (1) tends to take a while to wind up, missing the placings two back but running on to last time finishing third (22.20) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Expected to feature in the finish again. FREE SETTLER (2) jumped from this box last time and also the same course and distance when a one length second (25.68) in a Grade 5. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. BENTLEY OLAF (3) could manage only seventh at this track last time but caught the eye when clocking a superb 19.65 over 366m at Capalaba the start prior. Has the ability and can find winning form again. RITZA RINGER (8) will be hard to beat despite making his debut at this circuit.",
